Package: bioanchor
Title: Permanent Archiving of MCMC Analysis Metadata on Arweave
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dohoon", "Kim", , "dkim@promptgenix.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-HERE"))
Description: Bridges Bayesian MCMC analysis in R with Arweave decentralized 
    storage for permanent, tamper-proof archiving of analysis metadata. 
    Extracts convergence diagnostics, posterior summaries, and model 
    specifications from 'Stan', 'brms', and 'coda' objects, then uploads 
    them as structured JSON to the Arweave permaweb.
